Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:46.43,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}Going Going Going Going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:56.56,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}心の底に泉があるの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.48,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}どんなに落ち込んでもまた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.48,0:21:03.78,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}透明なもので満たされていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:10.45,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}これって　これって　なんていう気持ちなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:16.29,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}熱くて　痛くて　くすぐったくて　涙が出そう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:22.09,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}風って　鳥って　私より自由かな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:28.76,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}翼がないなら走ってくわ　行きたいところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.02,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}できるよね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:36.10,TEXT JP TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur3}Going Going Going Going on!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.43,0:20:56.56,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}内心深处仍有一汩清泉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.56,0:20:59.48,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}无论心灵多么干涸
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.48,0:21:03.78,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}都会再次被透明之泉充满
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.66,0:21:10.45,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}这究竟  这究竟  该说是怎样的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.45,0:21:16.29,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}灼热的  难受的  羞涩的  眼泪像要溢出
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.29,0:21:22.09,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}风儿  鸟儿  是否比我更加自由
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.09,0:21:28.76,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}没有翅膀就箭步前行吧  直至憧憬的彼方
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.76,0:21:31.02,TEXT CH TOP,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs32\blur3}我能做到的
